{"tid":1581631,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[文宣] 住過係大陸結左緍生埋仔既外國人拍左段片講大陸","createTime":"2019-09-19T15:59:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T20:18:10.000Z","uid":290365,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f09f073747b05dd5ed3fda4773db1d5e84e1ee75","tid":1581631,"uid":290365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T15:59:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ed4ryYokLzU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Ded4ryYokLzU&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=1e592679\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ed4ryYokLzU</a><br />\n<br />\n佢話十年前左右大陸係幾好既地方<br />\n住得幾舒服塔車食野又平<br />\n甚至令佢覺得自己家鄉(美國)個鎮好落後<br />\n但佢見證住呢幾年大陸越黎越癲乜自由都冇哂<br />\n所以佢決定返家鄉住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文宣識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f14bee82e911deba293d19d699fe1cbd1d90053","tid":1581631,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T15:59:46.000Z","msg":"【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊-會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人-食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=43914c38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"09afd13d726927c6469fc1550d13af00bae3cb43","tid":1581631,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:00:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf8e83bc03cb785d8b36e8d30e8dd7cde0228